To install it, first follow the instruction in /README

Then deploy a nice php/mysql/apache (or whatever) virtual host, that should point to /campaign/

configure a mysql database in campaign/config.php.sample, which should be renamed to config.php

ensure that the .htaccess is taken into account by your webserver, and that rewrite rules are enabled.

clone the plivo-helper files into campaign/plivo by using : 

cd campaign/
git clone https://github.com/digination/plivohelper-php plivo

inject piphone.sql into your database to create the basic structure

